in `configuration.nix`

``` nix
services = {
  ollama = {
    enable = true;
    host = "0.0.0.0"; # to access from other machines
    # package = pkgs.ollama-rocm; # use with AMD
    # or nvidia (find the option from nix options)
  };
};
```
